|url = http://sankei.jp.msn.com/culture/imperial/080927/imp0809270809000-n2.htm 
|title = 【皇室ウイークリー】（４７）雅子さま、絵画展をご鑑賞　承子さまは早大ご入学 |publisher = 産経新聞 |date = 2008-09-27 |accessdate = 2022-06-26 |archivedate = 2008-10-03
|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081003015841/http://sankei.jp.msn.com/culture/imperial/080927/imp0809270809000-n2.htm}}</ref>，
2013年畢業。亦入選美國[[富比世|富比世]]雜誌「The 20 Hottest Young Royals」，是根據未婚皇族中「國際網路與媒體影響力」的排名<ref>{{cite news |language = en 
