2013年（平成25年）4月，就職於{{link-ja|日本聯合國兒童基金會委員會|日本ユニセフ協会}}<ref>{{cite news |language = ja |url = https://news.ntv.co.jp/category/society/224907 |title = 高円宮家・承子さま、日本ユニセフに就職へ |publisher = 日テレNEWS |date = 2013-03-15 |accessdate = 2022-06-26 |archivedate = 2022-05-16 |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516060822/https://news.ntv.co.jp/category/society/224907 }}</ref>。
